title: Double Trouble 2022: Chargers & Broncos
description:
Field Yates, Mike Clay and Daniel Dopp round out the AFC West with a Double Trouble on two of the most interesting fantasy rosters in the NFL with the Chargers and Broncos. Then, the crew welcomes in the newest member of the ESPN Fantasy team Liz Loza!
